<!--
	Definitions of the following jobs: 
		o AD2tbits Sync script scheduled to be run every 30 min.
		o TBits User DB Sync script scheduled to be run every 30 min.
		o Indexer Daemon scheduled to be run every 5 min.
		o Index Optimizer scheduled to be run every day at 06:00 AM.
		o DH-Cron that logs requests for data hyd every day at 06:00 AM.
		o Job to log request to TBits to add holidays for forthcoming year. 
